      "role": "user",
      "content": "everything is gone. the firm, the funding, the house... all of it. i just lost everything in the crash and the debt is so high i won't ever get out of it. i can't even think about going home. the look on my parents faces when they realize i blew everything... i just can't face that shame. i feel like a ghost already.",
