      "role": "user",
      "content": "thanks but it doesn't work like that. talking doesn't change the numbers in the bank account or the lawsuits. it doesn't make the shame go away. it just keeps the conversation on how big of a failure i am. \n\nsometimes i feel like the only way to actually stop the feeling is to just... stop everything. not just the business, but everything. like, if i'm not around to be a disappointment, then the shame isn't a problem anymore. wouldn't that be the only way to actually solve it? to just make the mistake disappear?",
